{"type": "article", "id": 27945, "title": "时尚奥斯卡颁奖，以及，阿迪 NMD 推出粉红色款｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-06-08T10:52:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 743, "name": "零售"}, {"id": 28765, "name": "购物体验"}, {"id": 11592, "name": "夏季"}, {"id": 139, "name": "涂鸦"}, {"id": 862, "name": "设计师"}, {"id": 25091, "name": "奥运"}, {"id": 5894, "name": "制服"}, {"id": 6419, "name": "Armani"}, {"id": 979, "name": "CFDA"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 6450, "name": "德勤"}, {"id": 4579, "name": "历峰集团"}, {"id": 1331, "name": "雅诗兰黛"}, {"id": 2823, "name": "Lacoste"}, {"id": 2840, "name": "Opening Ceremony"}, {"id": 1425, "name": "Saint Laurent"}, {"id": 22261, "name": "Revlon"}, {"id": 984, "name": "Coty"}, {"id": 15559, "name": "L'Oreal"}, {"id": 28236, "name": "revolve"}, {"id": 2200, "name": "Moschino"}, {"id": 129, "name": "Kate Moss"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702154618AWMKoeO6LkhZUCRm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2><b>一些重要的新闻：</b></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/6/6/11873496/2016-cfda-awards-winners\"><b>CFDA 大奖颁布</b></a>｜有时尚界的奥斯卡之称的“美国时装设计师协会大奖（CFDA Awards）”，近日在曼哈顿颁发 2016 年度奖项，主要获奖者名单如下——年度女装设计师：Marc Jacobs、年度男装设计师：Thom  Browne、年度配饰设计师： Mansur Gavriel 的 Rachel Mansur 和 Floriana Gavriel、国际大奖：Gucci 创意总监 Alessandro Michele、时尚偶像大奖：Beyoncé。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Revlon-acquires-Cutex-from-Coty-Inc-,700423.html\"><b>露华浓收购指甲油品牌 Cutex</b></a>｜露华浓集团（Revlon）近日宣布收购 Coty 集团旗下品牌 Cutex，此前露华浓仅拥有  Cutex 美国运营权，本次收购将完善露华浓对于 Cutex 世界范围内运营权的合并，有利于其业务的扩张。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Saint-Laurent-to-skip-Men-s-Fashion-Week-in-Paris,700766.html\"><b>Saint Laurent 将不会参加本季巴黎男装周</b></a>｜据巴黎 Vogue 报道，新艺术总监 Anthony Vaccarello 执导下的 Saint Laurent  将不会参加 2017 春夏巴黎男装周，而是九月与女装成衣秀合并。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Champions-of-luxury-2016-LVMH-Richemont-Estee-Lauder-lead,701034.html\"><b>德勤公布年度奢侈品牌排名</b></a>｜近日，德勤（Deloitte）2016 年度奢侈品排行榜单公布，法国 LVMH、瑞士历峰集团、美国雅诗兰黛集团仍旧保持去年的位置，依次位列前三。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/L-Oreal-USA-appoints-first-ever-Chief-Retail-Officer,701012.html\"><b> L'Oreal 美国任命首位首席零售官</b></a>｜继欧莱雅（ L’Oreal）加拿大地区上周任命了一位首席零售官（Chief Retail Officer ）后，欧莱雅美国地区周二也宣布 Marc-Alexandre Risch 将担任首位首席零售官，致力于提升顾客购物体验。</p>\n<h2><span style=\"text-align: left; background-color: transparent;\">一些值得一看的：</span></h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/armani-ea7-2016-olympic-uniform-campaign/\">Emporio Armani 为意大利国家队准备的 2016 里约热内卢奥运会制服</a>：<span style=\"text-align: left; background-color: transparent;\"><br></span></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154558zohqORMl5YULVx82.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154559zn3ZwTSGsRUqx5BI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/shoes/adidas-nmd-r1-vapor-pink/\"> adidas Originals NMD 推出粉红色款</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154559gPrz7awoF9exTR6p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154600CNJWyKEeYkXDi3hR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154601DKZrPgn0ltseuETU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/moschino-fall-2016-campaign/\">Moschino 拍摄 2016 秋冬大片</a>，女主角们的涂鸦充满反叛精神：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154602iGr07nXxKlZuPMVA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154602fPVxS9pdUzRIvmwq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154603yBjHWknzhQiFvwKU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154604fhvrlH6EUz13TOxa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/kate-moss-models-clothing-collab-edit/\">Kate Moss 为  Net-a-Porter 的 <i>The Edit</i> 杂志拍摄封面</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154605knoudDqXYrNaB3F8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154606FL9pY3BGUscdhbV8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154607NFJPoefrWKZ5qRzM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/6/7/11875204/lacoste-x-opening-ceremony-capsule-collection\" style=\"display: inline !important;\">Lacoste 和 Opening Ceremony 合作推出一个胶囊系列</a>，包括两款 Polo 裙、六款衬衫，灵感来自网球服饰以及 70 年代加州冲浪文化。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154607KZH7iSt563UTcC9E.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021546080QPIrCaDdyTzJYnh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021546088exhtB6gdHyDovac.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47742818\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154609hQZMAVbLcdPIo6S1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48122392\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154609m1tXL6CJKU5nxFWi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47771588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p> IT girl Nicole Richie 的首饰品牌  House of Harlow，近日<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/revolve-house-harlow-clothing-shop/\">与 REVOLVE  合作推出一个波西米亚风格的夏季胶囊系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021546109WSvufq3BPpOmKlz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154611TW7jei21OpNdZlDw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154613mpGyOdZQqIuKW2Ta.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021546141oYiS2tpLmOU6fkv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154615HQhUwVcj7r4GftgR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154616ZhnECVzw58sx20WK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154616vCAq4sKfIlWjMheZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75423729\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}